Summary: Late at night on my balcony its been 4 years but it was silent and had 5 vibrant lights underneath it.
divs: Sighting Detailslooking out into the ocean i notice to my left a flying object... It was almost a humming sound but very quiet almost as if it didnt exsist. It flew over me similiar in size to a commuter smaller wing span. Its was like a flying V... It then appeared to submerge in the ocean in the far horizon or it took off into space and its path appeared curved due to it leaving the atmosphere. Truley amazing i believe either in the technology or extra-terrestrial life sorry took so long to report i have been increasdingly involved in the history channel programs... acient aliens etc... I thank you for reading this if you do
